    <abstract>
      <t>The Congestion Measurement enables precise congestion control,
   assists in effective load balancing, and simplifies network debugging
   by accurately reflecting the degree of congestion across network
   paths.  This document defines how Congestion Measurement Data Fields
   are encapsulated in IPv6.</t>
